in any party.

743
01:18:57,165 --> 01:19:00,430
These feeble, bloodless people.

744
01:19:00,668 --> 01:19:05,298
These people need death above all.

745
01:19:05,540 --> 01:19:08,634
The blood that
incites a brother to grief

746
01:19:08,877 --> 01:19:12,210
the feeling of nothing
which leads to love.

747
01:19:12,447 --> 01:19:17,544
Death like faith, not like fear.

748
01:19:35,870 --> 01:19:37,269
Why, Paulo?

